witches Mother Malkin is a pit on the top of a mountain. Years later, she

castle that she restores with magic. She meets her sister Bony Lizzie and 
her niece Alice and plans to destroy Master Gregory to begin her kingdom of 
evil. Meanwhile the old hunter recruits the naive farmer Tom Ward, who is 
the seventh son of the seventh son of the Ward family, to team up with him 
and his partner Tusk to hunt down Mother Malkin. Tom's mother, who is 
secretly a good witch, gives a necklace with a magic stone to protect 
him. They head to the village where Tom meets Alice and falls in love 
with her. But what is the true intention of Alice? Will they succeed in
